{"tid":1612202,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"和理勇武都要轉型：勇武應該組隊，和理需要公投","createTime":"2019-10-02T07:32:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T17:11:20.000Z","uid":172081,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9f386ca80c6054ca23892e735e7f13cbda1e8a3d","tid":1612202,"uid":172081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T07:32:42.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">首先講勇武：</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n睇下下面嘅post：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1611770/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1611770/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1610829/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1610829/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1611989/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1611989/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>勇武需要組織上嘅升級。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n如果驚進退時人數不足或者想做嘢時冇人跟，最直接嘅解決方法係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">組隊</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n行動實行上、資訊流通程度以及資訊可靠性上，組隊發夢都一定好過單人發夢。<br />\n<br />\n如果熟悉嘅朋友中冇前線勇武，每次發夢時就留意下身邊有邊個做過嘅野令你覺得一定唔鬼嘅，就考慮去同對方組隊啦。<br />\n<br />\n有隊嘅話，亦可以<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">解鎖其他低風險行動</span></strong>如鶳、示威日程外攻擊特定商店、遠離主要地點的hit and run之類。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">至於和理非都有需要轉型：</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n和理非轉型方向好多，文宣轉型的必要性在於自己香港人同埋外國都對同樣嘅資訊同樣嘅宣傳方式麻木，所以 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">要諗新野。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n對內，至少之前商場內灑文宣落樓下可以 reach 到一啲睇夠連濃牆唔想再睇嘅人，可以再用用或睇吓有無方法再進一步。對外暫時無 idea，求 comment。<br />\n<br />\n另一樣好重要但係唔見有嘅係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">全民公投</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n有聲音話要直接民主，要成立臨時議會、臨時立法會、改組警隊等，我贊成，<br />\n<br />\n但實行上其中一個重大問題是<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">首二者要有公信力、要證明其認受性</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n而對內，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">證明其認受性只有公投一法。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n實行上暫時最有可能嘅方法係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">實體票站</span></strong>，因為只有咁樣先可以確認投票人為本人。<br />\n<br />\n至於票站運行安全問題我暫時提供唔到解決方法，要諗；民間公投時否合法我唔知，求指點。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></strong>"},{"pid":"8f8ee714895ae67fda096b8c93063bd373fa2789","tid":1612202,"uid":154486,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T07:35:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">公投呀<br />\n<br />\n票站呀<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"ecf54c329e90b210ab3e45a9ed32a4b20c66fefa","tid":1612202,"uid":154486,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9f386ca80c6054ca23892e735e7f13cbda1e8a3d","tid":1612202,"uid":172081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T07:32:42.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">首先講勇武：</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n睇下下面嘅post：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1611770/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1611770/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1610829/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1610829/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1611989/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1611989/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>勇武需要組織上嘅升級。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n如果驚進退時人數不足或者想做嘢時冇人跟，最直接嘅解決方法係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">組隊</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n行動實行上、資訊流通程度以及資訊可靠性上，組隊發夢都一定好過單人發夢。<br />\n<br />\n如果熟悉嘅朋友中冇前線勇武，每次發夢時就留意下身邊有邊個做過嘅野令你覺得一定唔鬼嘅，就考慮去同對方組隊啦。<br />\n<br />\n有隊嘅話，亦可以<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">解鎖其他低風險行動</span></strong>如鶳、示威日程外攻擊特定商店、遠離主要地點的hit and run之類。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">至於和理非都有需要轉型：</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n和理非轉型方向好多，文宣轉型的必要性在於自己香港人同埋外國都對同樣嘅資訊同樣嘅宣傳方式麻木，所以 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">要諗新野。</span>